  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Tutorial_GM_AfterFire
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - There. All four core elements are yours.
  - I name you a Novice. You may begin using the alchemy table to fuse new elements.
  - Don't get ahead of yourself. At your rank only a handful of recipes will answer you. Climb higher, and more will reveal themselves.
  - Try your hand at mud. See if you can guess which two elements make it.
